<br>
Your healer just cant keep up with your rate of hp loss. (these new kunark mobs especially, take us out fast)<br>
<br>
In emergency EVAC situations(which are more frequent now in Kunark)  other casters, instead of taunting mobs off of the EVAC person so that they can cast it, will cast their personal gate instead. (this peeves the evacers and tanks)<br>
